subSubSection.paragraph:
Distribution. Recent, usually found on hard substrata at 60–100 m depth in the fjords of west Norway , in the Barents Sea, on the west coast of Greenland , Faroe Islands , northwest Scotland and Icelandic waters (
Fig. 1
).
